{"tid":706396,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【推介】now 新聞台 經緯線：《旺角六月》衞碧君","createTime":"2018-06-17T23:08:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T20:05:06.000Z","uid":147314,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e468b74e9f6318ec3eba9238aa0acb576f02e44d","tid":706396,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T23:08:26.000Z","msg":"提要版：3:20 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=309757\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D309757&d=%2FO3HsluWmFOAV2OYkmdD8gtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=c9f10b02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D309757&h=262b94e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=309757</a><br />\n<br />\n成集：16:40 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=309773\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D309773&d=%2FO3HsluWmFOAV2OYkmdD8gtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=4a11882e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D309773&h=d38950de\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=309773</a>"},{"pid":"e780ffb4718bdb3bcc2e39e869bd77a597ad82c4","tid":706396,"uid":147314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T23:09:37.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】旺角騷亂發生之後，包括梁天琦在內的多名年輕人，暴動罪成被重囚。三名曾經站在前線，關心政治的年輕人：見證旺角騷亂的紀實攝影師凱撒、曾經是本民前發言人的衞碧君，以及打正本土旗號的前大學學生會幹事袁德智，在沉澱過後，他們在六月初夏重返旺角，細說這兩年來心態上的轉變，重新思考抗爭之路。<br />\n<br />\n中大藝術系二年級學生凱撒一直熱衷紀實攝影，兩年前的年初一，他用相機記錄了旺角騷亂。<br />\n<br />\n凱撒曾經是學民思潮成員，在反國教集會中更一度參與絕食，但近這幾年，他改用創作的形式例如舉辦相展、拍攝紀錄片，繼續關注社會。<br />\n<br />\n十九歲的衞碧君曾經是本土民主前線的發言人，她說很多參與社運的朋友因為街頭抗爭遭受挫折，而變得很悲觀。<br />\n<br />\n衞碧君後來退出本民前，同時專心修讀高級文憑課程，很快就會畢業。她稱，這兩年都有反思勇武抗爭手法是否適合現時的香港，但強調自己的立場沒有動搖。<br />\n<br />\n多名社運人士因為暴動罪被判入獄，今晚播出的《經緯線》，幾位年輕人會重新思考旺角騷亂之後怎樣繼續抗爭。"},{"pid":"33f57cce379588188667ecad38c55282b84a6915","tid":706396,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T23:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5021ce796773304ce84127f0ca80c90f59391a9d","tid":706396,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T11:02:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"407337e3de06befbd9e2baa501795909479dff7b","tid":706396,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5021ce796773304ce84127f0ca80c90f59391a9d","tid":706396,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T11:02:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T11:12:36.000Z","msg":"有波路，台仰走佬浪費左"},{"pid":"1f5b492825598a84287b5ead32e875872ef645c0","tid":706396,"uid":147314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T19:54:36.000Z","msg":"會行動、會反省、會思考、唔放棄<br />\n<br />\n人才 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b8b08376b009700ac414b6ce232c8d2687fcb8b","tid":706396,"uid":104443,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T20:05:06.000Z","msg":"唔好放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當今世上所謂民主國家都係由自己人民辛辛苦苦爭返嚟，成就今日舉世聞名嘅自由國度。香港人都一定要做到呢一點，每一個人都有責任為自己嘅地方去付出，由自己手中建立理想國度，我地每個人抱住希望，做少少，積少成多，終有一日，一定會實現大家嘅理想"}]}